title: BIG FACTS LIVE feat. MONEY MAN & ERICA BANKS
itunes:title: BIG FACTS LIVE feat. MONEY MAN & ERICA BANKS
description:
The 1st Big Facts Live of 2022 was one for the history books. 

The Flow Queen, Erica Banks spoke with the crew about female unity, pet peeves, Nicki Minaj controversy and more. 

Arguably the biggest underground rapper out, Money Man spoke with Bank, Scream and Jade about financial literacy, shrooms, evolving from the streets to a businessman and more.
